# PrisonIL

[PrisonIL] is a [Minecraft](https://minecraft.net/ "Minecraft home") server, using [Spigot](http://www.spigotmc.org/ "Spigot home"), built for version `1.8.x`.

This server is public, __BUT IT'S WIP!!!__. If you want to help, the server IP is: `89.139.139.222:25565`!

[Server Website](http://prison-il.enjin.com "Hosted by Enjin.").
